# 🚀 Selvaganesh - AI/ML Developer Portfolio

![Portfolio Preview](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/portfolio-preview.png)

## 🌟 Overview

Welcome to my personal portfolio website! I'm **Selvaganesh**, a passionate B.Tech student in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning at Bannari Amman Institute of Technology (2022-2026) with a 7.2 CGPA. This portfolio showcases my journey as a dedicated AI/ML developer and problem-solver who loves exploring innovative technologies.

## 🎯 Live Demo

🔗 **[Visit My Portfolio](https://selvaprofile19.vercel.app)**

